{"tid":2028482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美參議員Ted Cruz: I’ve long said that HK is the new Berlin","createTime":"2020-05-21T23:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T03:37:47.000Z","uid":41998,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0669b9d6dd1f2a9c136fbc1a538a3ad76af4cf","tid":2028482,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:53:16.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I&rsquo;ve long said that Hong Kong is the new&nbsp;Berlin, and the United States&nbsp;must stand strong with our allies and hold the line against the spread of the Chinese Communist Party.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KbpVKTo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKbpVKTo.jpg&h=c1fedf78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenTedCruz/status/1263614774673317889?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenTedCruz%2Fstatus%2F1263614774673317889%3Fs%3D09&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=2bf8eda5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenTedCruz%2Fstatus%2F1263614774673317889%3Fs%3D09&h=eff404b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenTedCruz/status/1263614774673317889?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d097afe4aa44e458a6f5f8f7726592c5357d3f52","tid":2028482,"uid":215876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:53:39.000Z","msg":"我地要同共產黨對賭香港對世界經濟嘅影響力<br />\n賭美國守香港嘅決心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來佢地日日扮一國兩制<br />\n搞個假法治搵黑警濫捕<br />\n搵紅官亂判<br />\n班鬼佬都無乜位入香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而家支共直接插旗撕破埋假面具<br />\n今次係我地香港人最後生機<br />\n成件串埋港共 黑警 紅官 賣港狗（開始有狗話佢地只係奉命行事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奉命賣港殺人？）<br />\n<br />\n共產黨以一國一制搞亂香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到時外國想淨係制裁班共狗又好<br />\n成個香港制裁都好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地都無得輸<br />\n因為無野差得過跟住落嚟落入支那手<br />\n變新疆2.0"},{"pid":"553342c746a26ccd257373dda86e38884b2bc3c8","tid":2028482,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:57:49.000Z","msg":"無知一問點解係新柏林？<br />\n但睇佢講完好心噏"},{"pid":"6b395e3dac05fb7161f0b71e00c2be75019b351a","tid":2028482,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"553342c746a26ccd257373dda86e38884b2bc3c8","tid":2028482,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:57:49.000Z","msg":"無知一問點解係新柏林？<br />\n但睇佢講完好心噏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"如果英美法唔理 西柏林就會俾社會主義東德完全侵蝕<br />\n<br />\n如果英美唔理 香港就會..."},{"pid":"2003216a0be611933bfff4172618da2fdd4f2e5f","tid":2028482,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b395e3dac05fb7161f0b71e00c2be75019b351a","tid":2028482,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"553342c746a26ccd257373dda86e38884b2bc3c8","tid":2028482,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:57:49.000Z","msg":"無知一問點解係新柏林？<br />\n但睇佢講完好心噏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"如果英美法唔理 西柏林就會俾社會主義東德完全侵蝕<br />\n<br />\n如果英美唔理 香港就會..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:00:54.000Z","msg":"原來係冷戰，多謝絲打<br />\n將希望放係美國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317a8ad8d596736d0acb40eb50b8d895e6cd5b90","tid":2028482,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:06:33.000Z","msg":"當年東德點樣突然爆？"},{"pid":"6d67f9998703633fb6ae1c6a7c52d278b7a54f75","tid":2028482,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317a8ad8d596736d0acb40eb50b8d895e6cd5b90","tid":2028482,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:06:33.000Z","msg":"當年東德點樣突然爆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T00:09:33.000Z","